<div class="top-section">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 center">
			<%= image_tag("leksi_icon.png", alt: "Leksi Tree") %>
			<h3>
				A fun and simple way to build vocabulary.
			</h3>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-6 col-xs-offset-3 col-sm-2 col-sm-offset-5
								btn-custom-get-started center">
			<%= link_to "Get started", signup_path %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br>
	<div class="center">
		<small>Have an account?</small>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="thin-gray-section center">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
			<%= image_tag("leksi_icon.png", alt: "Leksi Tree") %>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-5">
			<h4>The best way to learn new words</h4>

			Learning with Leksi is simple and fun.
			With game-like features, our quick yet powerful word games, which are
			based on hard evidence on what it takes to really learn words,
			are the perfect dose for daily practice.

			<br>
			<br>

			<div>
				<%= link_to "See how we do it" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="fat-section">
	<h3 class="center">Gamification in every lesson</h3>

	<div class="gamification-container col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
		<div class="row center">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="gamification-first-image"></div>

				<h4>Game on!</h4>

				<p>
					First play the <em>Fundamentals</em> to learn the basics.
					Then kick it up a notch with <em>Leksi Jeopardy</em>. Finally,
					unleash your creativity with <em>Leksi Freestyle.</em>.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="gamification-second-image"></div>
				<h4>Checkpoints</h4>

				<p>
					Instantly see how well you know what you learn along the way.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="center">
			<%= link_to image_tag("leksi_icon.png") %>
		</div>

		<div class="row center">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="gamification-third-image"></div>

				<h4>Level Up</h4>

				<p>
					Earn experience points, level up, and achieve your weekly goals
					with each game you complete.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="gamification-fourth-image"></div>
				<h4>Leaderboard</h4>

				<p>
					It's one thing to climb the Leaderboard ranks and another to remain on
					top!
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
</div>

<div class="thin-gray-section">
	<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
		<div class="center">
			<%= image_tag("multiple_devices_light_black_100.png") %>
			<h4>Use Leksi on any software or device</h4>
		</div>

		Be more productive wherever you are, on the go. To use Leksi, all you need
		is a web browser (e.g. Safari, Chrome, Firefox) and internet access.
		This means you can use Leksi on a phone, tablet, laptop, or computer.
	</div>

	<div class="clear"></div>
</div>

<div class="fat-section">
	<%= render "static_pages/carousel" %>
</div>

<div class="thin-white-section">
	<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
		<div class="center">
			<%= image_tag("school_color_100.png", width: 230, height: 230) %>
			<h4>Leksi for Schools</h4>
		</div>

		Vocabulary is the biggest indicator of a student's success. See why
		it's crucial to not only literacy development, but also other academic
		areas as well.

		<p>
			<%= link_to "Bring Leksi to your classroom", "#" %>
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
